notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-25T07:28:41.581Z",claude-code-agent,"Exposed profiles through MCP + contracts + drift gates (delivered together with pm-v37g in one PR). Added narrow pm_profile MCP tool (tools count 27->28; updated mcp-handshake.spec EXPECTED_TOOL_NAMES + length, smoke-claude-plugin.mjs required list + count, smoke-claude-plugin.spec list, CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN.md \"28 tools\", server prose narrow-tool list). Added \"profile\" action: PM_TOOL_ACTIONS + PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES entry, PM_TOOL_ACTION_SCHEMA_CONTRACTS.profile entry (required subcommand; optional name/dryRun/author/force; conditionalRequired name for show+apply) so contracts --full does not crash buildActionScopedToolSchema, PROFILE_FLAG_CONTRACTS + resolver case + contracts.ts command->flags map, tool-definitions.ts pm_profile inputSchema. Regenerated tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json (contracts:check green). MCP routing case \"profile\" in server.runAction (list/show/apply + unknown throw) covered by profile-command integration spec (incl nested-options path). contracts:check, quality:static, docs-skills, typecheck all green."
